data.description: Exquisite custom home nestled on a sprawling one-acre lot, offering a tranquil country ambiance while being just minutes away from Tylertown's vibrant amenities. This captivating residence spans an expansive 2761 square feet of meticulously designed living space, featuring four bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a host of luxurious amenities. The interior showcases stunning cabinetry, soaring cathedral ceilings, an inviting office space, and an upstairs area that houses one of the bedrooms. The well-appointed kitchen seamlessly transitions into the spacious living room, creating an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment. Hardwood floors grace the majority of the home, adding warmth and elegance.  Outside, the front porch provides a picturesque vantage point, offering views of majestic hardwoods dotting the yard and the paved driveway. At the rear, a charming back porch overlooks the private, fenced-in backyard, complete with a superbly crafted heated and cooled "she shed" perfect for pursuing hobbies or additional storage. The expansive one-acre lot also features a separate building for storing lawn and yard equipment. Completing this remarkable property is a matching on-slab garage, adding both convenience and charm to the overall appeal. This is a truly exceptional opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and rural serenity, all within reach of Tylertown's conveniences and attractions.
